cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.IT, cs.CR, cs.SY

The paper discusses the use of artificial intelligence techniques for cognitive routing in cognitive radio networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also extensively discusses decision-theoretic and learning techniques from the field of AI, making cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) a likely category as well. The paper also touches upon information theory (cs.IT), cognitive radio (cs.CR), and system and control theory (cs.SY) in the context of cognitive routing.
